citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:10pm-2:40pm on
10 February 2022. Arrived at facility, called and left a message for the manager, waited for half an hour and left a note on
the door. Received a call back after leaving the facility, discussed adjusted optimal hours and attempted inspection
report.
End Section
